                                                                                                                                                        1. Basic requirements

                                                                                                                                                          Requeriments to run this system in your server.

                                                                                                                                                          Hardware settings may vary according to the number of processes.

                                                                                                                                                          • HTTP Server (with PHP >= 5.4)
                                                                                                                                                          • PHP: PDO Extension
                                                                                                                                                          • PHP: PDO MySQL Driver
                                                                                                                                                          • MySQL Server
                                                                                                                                                          • MySQL: Database
                                                                                                                                                          • jQuery: version => 1.7
                                                                                                                                                          • All folders are allowed to create, change and delete

                                                                                                                                                          1. Best practices

                                                                                                                                                            1. Bandwidth usage

                                                                                                                                                              The bandwidth usage can be an important factor if your server can not spend much, so we recommend using update values according to your needs, values between 1000 and 3000 milliseconds guarantee a live experience, however the bandwidth usage is considerable.

                                                                                                                                                              Examples of how to change:

                                                                                                                                                              1. Add this line in a script tag after the "js.php" script be loaded: 

                                                                                                                                                                            
<head>    
    <script src="mechat/php/js.php" type="text/javascript"></script>  
    <script>    
        meChat_Settings({
            box_update_timer: 5000 //Time in milliseconds to update chatboxes
        });   
    </script>   
</head>
                                                                                                                                                              2. Configuration file "mechat/php/config.php": 

                                                                                                                                                                            
<?php
    # End of code
    
    $me_chat_config['me_chat_settings']['box_update_timer'] = 5000;

    # Rest of the code    
?>

                                                                                                                                                              1. Stylesheet

                                                                                                                                                                It is very important to have discipline in order to modify any style of a system, and this also applies to the meChat, is recommended that you let the style files unchanged and that if change something, create a second file... It will be easier to upgrade the system...

                                                                                                                                                                Example:

                                                                                                                                                                Add this line after the "js.php" script be loaded: 
                                                                                                                                                                    
<head>    
    <script src="mechat/php/js.php" type="text/javascript"></script>  
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="mechat/css/templates/example.css">
</head>


                                                                                                                                                                Stylesheet "mechat/css/templates/example.css": 
                                                                                                                                                                    
.me-chat > *
{
    font-family: "Times New Roman";
}

                                                                                                                                                                1. Viewport

                                                                                                                                                                  For better mobile experience is recommended to use a Viewport which the zoom is not allowed and responsive possibility is permitted.

                                                                                                                                                                  Add this line in the <head>: 

                                                                                                                                                                      
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">

                                                                                                                                                                2. Functions

                                                                                                                                                                  1. Javascript

                                                                                                                                                                    1. Chatboxes

                                                                                                                                                                      1. Chatboxes Properties

                                                                                                                                                                        The properties of chatboxes, brings to developer new possibilities, for customization and automation of the chatboxes.

                                                                                                                                                                        Native properties:

                                                                                                                                                                        • id - User id of friend/user (string/int)
                                                                                                                                                                        • name - User name of friend/user (string)
                                                                                                                                                                        • picture - User picture of friend/user (string)
                                                                                                                                                                        • lastupdate - Last update of chatbox, in timestamp (int)
                                                                                                                                                                        • createdorder - Order of creation of the chatbox (int)
                                                                                                                                                                        • unread - Total of unread messages of the chatbox (int)
                                                                                                                                                                        • flash - Enable flash notification (bool)
                                                                                                                                                                        • displayed - Is displayed (bool)
                                                                                                                                                                        • hidden - Is hidden (bool)
                                                                                                                                                                        • lastmessage - Last message of chatbox (string)
                                                                                                                                                                        • lastmessage_ajax - Last message with data returned via AJAX (object)
                                                                                                                                                                        • loadingoldmessages - Is loading old messages (bool)

                                                                                                                                                                        * The native properties can be obtained with meChat_getProp(chatID, property); or the meChat_Event(event, function(chatID, chatDOM, chatProp) {});

                                                                                                                                                                        Examples of how to get properties:

                                                                                                                                                                        1. meChat_getProp(chatID, property); 

                                                                                                                                                                                  
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="alert( meChat_getProp('6', 'lastmessage') );">Show last message</a>
                                                                                                                                                                        2. meChat_Event(event, function(chatID, chatDOM, chatProp) {}); 

                                                                                                                                                                                  
<script>                 
    meChat_Event( 'chat.receivemessage chat.sendmessage', function( chatID, chatDOM, chatProp ) {
        
        alert(meChat_getProp(chatID, 'lastmessage')); //Shows the last message in the form of alert
        
        alert(chatProp.lastmessage); //It is equal to use: alert(meChat_getProp(chatID, 'lastmessage'));
        
    } );
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                        * The properties can be changed and created using meChat_setProp(chatID, property, value);

                                                                                                                                                                        Examples of how to set or create the properties:

                                                                                                                                                                        1. Setting 

                                                                                                                                                                                  
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="meChat_setProp('6', 'flash', true);">Enable flash notification</a>
                                                                                                                                                                        2. Creating 

                                                                                                                                                                                  
<script>                 
    meChat_Event( 'chat.receivemessage', function( chatID, chatDOM, chatProp ) {
        
        var timestamp = meChat_timestamp(); //Get and store the current timestamp
        
        meChat_setProp(chatID, 'lastreceivedmessage', timestamp); //Create and set the property "lastreceivedmessage" with the value of the variable timestamp
        
    } );
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                          Description This function was created to close a chatbox. Syntax meChat_Close( string/int chatID );

                                                                                                                                                                          chatID - User id of friend/user                                                                                                                                                                           Return undefined (string)

                                                                                                                                                                          Examples:

                                                                                                                                                                          1. Using in <script> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                        
<script>         
    $('#button-close').click(function(){
        meChat_Close('6');
    });
</script>
                                                                                                                                                                          2. Using in <a> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                        
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="meChat_Close('6');">Close chat</a>

                                                                                                                                                                          1. meChat_Event(event, function)

                                                                                                                                                                            Description This function is called every time an event occurs with the chatbox. Syntax meChat_Event( string event, function( chatID, chatDOM, chatProp ) {} );

                                                                                                                                                                            Events:
                                                                                                                                                                            1. chat.open - When the chatbox is opened
                                                                                                                                                                            2. chat.close - When the chatbox is closed
                                                                                                                                                                            3. chat.sendmessage - When sending message
                                                                                                                                                                            4. chat.receivemessage - When receiving message
                                                                                                                                                                            5. chat.body.click - When click on the body of the chatbox

                                                                                                                                                                            Arguments of the internal function
                                                                                                                                                                            1. this - User id of friend/user
                                                                                                                                                                            2. chatID - User id of friend/user
                                                                                                                                                                            3. chatDOM - DOM element of chatbox
                                                                                                                                                                            4. chatProp - Chatbox properties
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Return undefined (string)

                                                                                                                                                                            Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                
<script>         
    meChat_Event( 'chat.receivemessage chat.sendmessage', function( chatID, chatDOM, chatProp ) {
    
        $(chatDOM).hide(); //Hide the chatbox
        
        meChat_alertMessage(this, 'Message!', 4000); //chatID and this  equals
        
        alert(meChat_getProp(chatID, 'lastmessage')); //Shows the last message in the form of alert
        
        alert(chatProp.lastmessage); //It is equal to use: alert(meChat_getProp(chatID, 'lastmessage'));
        
    } );
</script>

Syntax meChat_alertMessage( string/int chatID, string message, int time );

                                                                                                                                                                                  chatID - User id of friend/user

                                                                                                                                                                                  Recommendation: "message" must be less than 16 characters.
                                                                                                                                                                                  Important: "time" must be in milliseconds.                                                                                                                                                                                   Return undefined (string)

Using in <script> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                                
<script>         
    $('#button-alert').click(function(){

    });
</script>

Using in <a> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                                
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="meChat_alertMessage('6', 'Alert text', 6000);">Alert text</a>

                                                                                                                                                                                      1. meChat_receiveDOMMessage(chatID, message, notifications, oldmessages)

                                                                                                                                                                                        Description This function was created to add the received messages within the chatbox. Syntax meChat_receiveDOMMessage( string/int chatID, string message, bool notifications = true, bool oldmessages = false );

                                                                                                                                                                                        chatID - User id of friend/user
                                                                                                                                                                                        message - Message to add to the body of the chatbox
                                                                                                                                                                                        notifications - Enable notification sound and flash (Default: true)
                                                                                                                                                                                        oldmessages - (Default: false)
                                                                                                                                                                                        1. true - Adds the message to the top
                                                                                                                                                                                        2. false - Adds the message to the bottom

                                                                                                                                                                                        Important: This function does not receive real messages.                                                                                                                                                                                         Return undefined (string) - Repeated message.
                                                                                                                                                                                        DOM element - If success to add.

                                                                                                                                                                                        Examples:

                                                                                                                                                                                        1. Using in <script> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<script>         
    $('#button-receive-test').click(function(){
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', false, true); //Add to the top without notification
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', true, true); //Add to the top with notification
        
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', false); //Add to the bottom without notification
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message'); //Add to the bottom with notification
        
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', false, false); //Add to the bottom without notification
        meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', true, false); //Add to the bottom with notification
    });
</script>
                                                                                                                                                                                        2. Using in <a> tag 

                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="meChat_receiveDOMMessage('6', 'Test message', true, false);">Add test message to the bottom with notification</a>

                                                                                                                                                                                              2. Cookies

                                                                                                                                                                                                1. Cookies Properties

                                                                                                                                                                                                  The properties of cookies from the meChat, brings to developer new possibilities, for customization and automation of the chatboxes.

                                                                                                                                                                                                  Native properties:

                                                                                                                                                                                                  • disable_notifications - Disable flash notifications of the chatboxes (bool) (Default: false)
                                                                                                                                                                                                  • disable_sounds - Disable sounds of chatboxes (bool) (Default: false)

                                                                                                                                                                                                  * The native properties can be obtained with meChatCookie_getProp(property);

                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example of how to get properties:


                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="alert( meChatCookie_getProp('disable_notifications') );">Show me value of disable_notifications</a>


                                                                                                                                                                                                  * The properties can be changed and created using meChatCookie_setProp(property, value);

                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example of how to set or create the properties:

                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<script>                 
    $(document).ready(function() {
        meChatCookie_setProp('disable_sounds', true); //Disable sounds of chatboxes
    });
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                      2. Menu

                                                                                                                                                                                                        1. meChatMenu_Open()

                                                                                                                                                                                                          Description This function was created to add and show the menu of chatboxes.

                                                                                                                                                                                                          Important: If this function is called after a chatbox has been opened, will have to use meChat_Order(); to organize the chatboxes.                                                                                                                                                                                                           Syntax meChatMenu_Open(); Return undefined (string)

                                                                                                                                                                                                          Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                          
<script>                       
    $(document).ready(function() {

    });
</script>

Syntax meChatMenu_Title( string title );

                                                                                                                                                                                                          2. Menu Tab

                                                                                                                                                                                                            1. meChatTab_Add(tabName)

                                                                                                                                                                                                              Description This function was created to add tabs in the menu of chatboxes.
                                                                                                                                                                                                              Important: The width of the tabs are in accordance with its quantity.

                                                                                                                                                                                                              Example:
                                                                                                                                                                                                              1. tab - width 100.00%
                                                                                                                                                                                                              2. tab - width 50.00%
                                                                                                                                                                                                              3. tab - width 33.33%
                                                                                                                                                                                                              4. tab - width 25.00%
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Syntax meChatTab_Add(tabName);

                                                                                                                                                                                                              tabName - Name of the tab

                                                                                                                                                                                                              Recommendation: "tabName" must be less than 8 characters.                                                                                                                                                                                                               Return id of created tab (int)

                                                                                                                                                                                                              Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                              
<script>                       
    $(document).ready(function() {
        meChatMenu_Open();
        meChatTab_Add('Tab 1');
        meChatTab_Add('Tab 2');
        meChatTab_Add('Tab 3');
    });
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                              1. meChatTab_Function(tabID, event, function)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                Description This function is called every time an event occurs with tab of the chatboxes menu. Syntax meChatTab_Function( int tabID, string event, function(tabID, tabDOM) {} );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                tabID - ID of the tab to be add function

                                                                                                                                                                                                                Events:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                1. click - When click on the tab
                                                                                                                                                                                                                2. touchstart - When touch on the tab
                                                                                                                                                                                                                3. mouseenter - When hover on the tab

                                                                                                                                                                                                                Arguments of the internal function
                                                                                                                                                                                                                1. tabID - ID of the tab
                                                                                                                                                                                                                2. tabDOM - DOM element of the tab
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Return false (bool) - If the tab does not exist.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                true (bool) - If found and added.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
<script>         
    $(document).ready(function() {
        meChatMenu_Open();
        meChatTab_Add('Tab 1');
        meChatTab_Add('Tab 2');
        var tab = meChatTab_Add('Tab 3'); //Add and store the tab id
        
        meChatTab_Function(tab, 'click touchstart', function(tabID, tabDOM){
        
            alert('You clicked on the tab with id: ' + tabID);
        
        });
    });
</script>

Syntax meChatTab_Remove( int tabID );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                  true (bool) - If found and removed.

<script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                    1. meChatTab_Show(tabID)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Description This function was created to show the contents of the tab (items) of chatboxes menu. Syntax meChatTab_Show( int tabID );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                      tabID - ID of the tab to show content                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Return false (bool) - If the tab does not exist.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                      true (bool) - If found and displayed.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
<script>    
    var tabFriends = 0; //Store the tab id
    
    $(document).ready(function() {

        tabFriends = meChatTab_Add('Friends'); //Save the tab id
    });

        meChatTab_Show(tabFriends); //Show the contents of the tab of friends  
    });
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                      1. meChatTab_Visibility(tabID)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Description This function was created to check if the content of tab is visible. Syntax meChatTab_Visibility(tabID);

                                                                                                                                                                                                                        tabID - ID of the tab to check if is visible                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Return false (bool) - If the tab is not visible.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                        true (bool) - If the tab is visible.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
<script>                       
    var tabFriends = 0; //Store the tab id
    
    $(document).ready(function() {
        meChatMenu_Open();
        
        tabFriends = meChatTab_Add('Friends'); //Save the tab id
        meChatTab_Show(tabFriends); //Show the contents of the tab of friends 
    });
    
    $('#button-isvisible').click(function() {
        if(meChatTab_Visibility(tabFriends) == true)
        {
            alert('Tab Friends is visible!');
        }
    });
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                          1. meChatTab_ItemFunction(itemID, event, function)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Description This function is called every time an event occurs with tab item of the chatboxes menu. Syntax meChatTab_ItemFunction( int itemID, string event, function(itemID, itemDOM) {} );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                            itemID - ID of the tab item to be add function

                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Events:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            1. click - When click on the tab item
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            2. touchstart - When touch on the tab item
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            3. mouseenter - When hover on the tab item

                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Arguments of the internal function
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            1. itemID - ID of the tab item
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            2. itemDOM - DOM element of the tab item
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Return false (bool) - If the item does not exist.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                            true (bool) - If found and added.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
<script>

        meChatTab_Add('Tab 1');

        meChatTab_ItemFunction(item, 'click touchstart', function(itemID, itemDOM){
        
            alert('You clicked on the item with id: ' + tabID);
        
        });
    });
</script>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  1. meChat_date(format, timestamp)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Description This function was created to format the string with timestamp. Syntax meChat_date( string format, int timestamp );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    format - String to be formatted
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "h" Hours - with leading zeros - 01,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "H" Hours - without leading zeros - 1,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "i" Minutes - with leading zeros - 00,59
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "I" Minutes - without leading zeros - 0,59
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "s" Seconds - with leading zeros - 00,59
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "S" Seconds - without leading zeros - 0,59
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "y" Year - Full Year - 2014,2015,2016
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "Y" Year - last two numbers - 14,15,16
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "m" Month - with leading zeros - 01,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "M" Month - without leading zeros - 1,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "d" Day - with leading zeros - 01,31
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "D" Day - without leading zeros - 1,31
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "a" Ante meridiem & Post meridiem - lowercase (am,pm)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "A" Ante meridiem & Post meridiem - uppercase (AM,PM)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    timestamp - Timestamp in UTC format                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Return string formatted (string)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="alert( meChat_date('G:i A', meChat_timestamp()) );">Show me the current time</a>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            1. Messages

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              1. meChatLogged_markAllAsRead($chatID)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Description This function was created to mark all messages of the logged user with another user as read. Syntax meChatLogged_markAllAsRead( string/int $chatID );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                $chatID - User id of friend/user                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Return false (bool) - If is not logged in or error in the query
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                true (bool) - If successfully executed

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6
    $user1 = meChatLogged(); // Saves the user id if logged
    
    $user2 = meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Creates the user and saves the id
    
    meChat_sendMessage($user2, $user1, 'I am a phoenix. Bwahahaha'); // John Phoenix sends a message
    meChat_sendMessage(user1, $user2, 'LOL! ROFTL!'); // John Phoenix receives a message
    
    meChatLogged_markAllAsRead($user2); // Mark all messages with John Phoenix as read
?>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                1. meChatLogged_receiveMessage($chatID, $starting, $method = true, $order = true, $limit = 20)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Description This function was created to get the last messages or the newest messages of the logged user with another user. Syntax meChatLogged_receiveMessage( string/int $chatID, int $starting, bool $method = true, bool $order = true, int $limit = 20 );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $chatID - User id of friend/user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $starting - From a reference (id of the message)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $method - (Default: true)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  1. true - above the reference
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  2. false - below the reference

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $order - (Default: true)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  1. true - the oldest messages to the most recent
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  2. false - the most recent message to the oldest

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  $limit - Maximum results (Default: 20)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Return false (bool) - If is not logged in or user does not exists

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  array (only with the user info) - If there error with the query
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example: 

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Array
(
    [id] => 7
    [name] => 'John Phoenix'
    [picture] => 'http://'
    [lastupdate] => 1456753395
)


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  array - Containing messages and info of the user, if successfully executed
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example: 

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Array
(
    [id] => 7
    [name] => 'John Phoenix'
    [picture] => 'http://'
    [lastupdate] => 1456753395
    [messages] => Array
        (
            [0] => Array
                (
                    [from] => 7
                    [message] => Array
                        (
                            [id] => 1004
                            [from_user_id] => 7
                            [to_user_id] => 6
                            [message] => 'I am a phoenix. Bwahahaha'
                            [date_timestamp] => 1456753391
                            [read] => 0
                            [read_timestamp] => -1
                        )

                )
        )
)




                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6
    $user1 = meChatLogged(); // Saves the user id if logged
    
    $user2 = meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Creates the user and saves the id
    
    meChat_sendMessage($user2, $user1, 'I am a phoenix. Bwahahaha'); // John Phoenix sends a message
    meChat_sendMessage($user1, $user2, 'LOL! ROFTL!'); // John Phoenix receives a message
    
    var_dump(meChatLogged_receiveMessage($user2, 0));
?>

Syntax meChatLogged_recentlyMessages( int $minutes = 10 );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    $minutes - Minutes before (Default: 10)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Return false (bool) - If is not logged in
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    array (empty) - If there error with the query

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    array - Containing messages, if successfully executed:

        [id] => 1004

        [message] => 'I am a phoenix. Bwahahaha'
        [date_timestamp] => 1456753391
        [read] => 0
        [read_timestamp] => -1
    )
)




                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      1. meChat_ListConversations($where = null, $order = null, $page = 0, $max_results = 10)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Description This function was created to return the conversations list. Syntax meChat_ListConversations( array $where = null, array $order = null, string/int $page = 0, string/int $max_results = 10 );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $where - Condition (Default: null)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Examples:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        1. array("id" => ">= 1", "read" => "= 0")

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $order - Sort results (Default: null)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Examples:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        1. array("id" => "ASC", "read_timestamp" => "DESC")
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        2. array("id" => "ASC")

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $page - Page (Default: 0)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $max_results - Maximum results (Default: 10)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Return false (bool) - If there error with the query

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        array - Conversations list, if successfully executed:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Example: 

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
Array
(
    [0] => Array
        (
            [id] => 1
            [from_user_id] => 3
            [to_user_id] => 1
            [message] => Hi Brother!

            [date_timestamp] => 1460255999
            [read] => 0
            [read_timestamp] => -1
        )

    [1] => Array
        (
            [id] => 2
            [from_user_id] => 3
            [to_user_id] => 1
            [message] => kk

            [date_timestamp] => 1460257203
            [read] => 0
            [read_timestamp] => -1
        )
)




                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
<?php    

    var_dump(meChat_ListConversations(null, null, 0, 10)); // All messages
    
    var_dump(meChat_ListConversations(array("read" => "= 0"), null, 0, 10)); // All unread conversations
    
    var_dump(meChat_ListConversations(array("read" => "= 0"), array("id" => "DESC"), 0, 10)); // All unread conversations, descending order
    
?>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                1. meChatLogged()

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Description This function was created to check if the user is logged. Syntax meChatLogged(); Return false (bool) - If not logged
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  user id (int) - If logged

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6
    
    if(meChatLogged() !== false) // If successfully logged
    {
        echo 'Logged!';
        $user1 = meChatLogged(); // Saves the user id if logged
        
        $user2 = meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Creates the user and saves the id
        
        meChat_sendMessage($user2, $user1, 'I am a phoenix. Bwahahaha'); // John Phoenix sends a message to user id 6
    }
?>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            1. meChat_Friendship($chatID, $chatID2)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Description This function was created to check friendship. Syntax meChat_Friendship( string/int $chatID, string/int $chatID2 );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $chatID - User id of user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              $chatID2 - User id of friend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               Return false (bool) - If there error with the query or are not friends
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              true (bool) - If are friends

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6
    $user1 = meChatLogged(); // Saves the user id if logged
    
    $user2 = meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Creates the user and saves the id
    
    meChat_AddFriend($user1, $user2); // John Phoenix and user id 6 are friends
    if(meChat_Friendship($user1, $user2))
    {
        echo 'John Phoenix and user id 6 are friends !';
    }
    
    meChat_RemoveFriend($user2, $user1); // John Phoenix and user id 6 are not friends
    if(meChat_Friendship($user1, $user2) == false)
    {
        echo 'John Phoenix and user id 6 are not friends !';
    }    
?>
