                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $chatID - User id of user
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      $chatID2 - User id of friend                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Return false (bool) - If there error with the query
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      true (bool) - If successfully executed

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
<?php
    meChat_Login('6'); // Login as id 6
    $user1 = meChatLogged(); // Saves the user id if logged
    
    $user2 = meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Creates the user and saves the id
    
    meChat_AddFriend($user1, $user2); // John Phoenix and user id 6 are friends
    
    meChat_RemoveFriend($user2, $user1); // John Phoenix and user id 6 are not friends
?>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      1. meChat_Update($chatID, $property, $value)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Description This function was created to update user information. Syntax meChat_Update( string/int $chatID, string $property, string $value );

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $chatID - User id to be update

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $property - Property to be set
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        1. identifier - User identifier
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        2. name - Username
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        3. picture - URL of user picture
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        4. lastupdate - Last update of the user, in timestamp

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        $value - Value to be assigned                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Return false (bool) - If the user does not exists or the property/column not exists
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        true (int) - If successfully executed

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Example:


                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
<?php
    meChat_Add('phoenix_xyz', 'John Phoenix', 'http://'); // Create a user
    
    $user = meChat_Identifier('phoenix_xyz'); // Get user id by identifier
    
    meChat_Update($user, 'name', 'John P.'); // Now the user name is John P.
?>

Getting started

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Installation: Installer

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    1. Extract the meChat folder in the root of your site.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2. Open in your browser "mechat/manager/index.php".
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat/manager/index.php

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    3. Login with the default password "123456".

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    4. Open in your browser "mechat/manager/installer.php".
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat/manager/installer.php

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    5. Change the password of manager in "mechat/manager/changepassword.php".
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat/manager/changepassword.php

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    6. Ready! Add the following line of code on pages where you want the meChat appear.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Exemple:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <!-- Rest of the code -->
        
        <script src="mechat/php/js.php" type="text/javascript"></script>

        <!-- Rest of the code -->        
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- Rest of the code -->
    </body>
</html>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Installation: Manual

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    1. Extract the meChat folder in the root of your site.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    2. Create a database with the name of your choice.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    3. Run the query "SQL.sql" found in the root folder of meChat in the database created.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    4. Set the database, image upload, and style of the meChat in the file "config.json" found in the "php" folder, which is located at the root of meChat.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat/config.json

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    5. Then open the manager of the meChat in your browser, this is located in the "manager" folder at the root of meChat. Check if everything is right, the default password is "123456".
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Example: www.yoursite.com/mechat/manager/index.php

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    6. Ready! Add the following line of code on pages where you want the meChat appear.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Exemple:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
<!DOCTYPE html>

        <!-- Rest of the code -->        
    </head>

        <!-- Rest of the code -->
    </body>
</html>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Example of adding to your system

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    The process to integrate the meChat to your site may seem hard, but it is not.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
<?php

# Rest of the code

include('mechat/php/functions.php'); // Include PHP functions of the meChat

$user_info = array(); // "$user_info" stores information of the logged user (Example)
$user_info['nickname'] = 'jason.darc'; // Nickname of the logged user
$user_info['name'] = 'Jason Darc'; // Name of the logged user
echo "Logged with successfully";

if(meChat_Identifier($user_info['nickname']) === false) // User with identifier "jason.darc" not exists
{

    $chatID = meChat_Add( // Create a user and store his chatID in the $chatID variable
        
        $user_info['nickname'], // Identifier
        $user_info['name'], // User name
        'http://' //User picture
        
    );
    
    meChatLogin($chatID); // Login by chatID
    
}
else
{

    $chatID = meChat_Identifier($user_info['nickname']); // Find and store the chatID by the identifier
    
    meChatLogin($chatID); // Login by chatID
    
}

# Rest of the code 

?>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "Y" Year - last two numbers - 14,15,16
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "m" Month - with leading zeros - 01,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "M" Month - without leading zeros - 1,12
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "d" Day - with leading zeros - 01,31
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "D" Day - without leading zeros - 1,31
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "a" Ante meridiem & Post meridiem - lowercase (am,pm)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            "A" Ante meridiem & Post meridiem - uppercase (AM,PM)
